  "title": "An oval multicolor UFO spotted at very low speed in Samambaia Sul-DF [1996]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/28/an-oval-multicolor-ufo-spotted-at-very-low-speed-in-samambaia-sul-df-1996/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-19S",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JUNE 6th, 1996</strong>. 18h30 pm. Duration: 30 minutes. When arriving at her residence in Samabaia Sul, Federal District, a woman observed an unidentified flying object 500 meters high. According to the witness, the UFO was also spotted by at least four other people nearby. The object was oval, white, green and red, about the size of &#8220;a helicopter approximately&#8221; and it was flying at a &#8220;slow, almost stopped&#8221; speed. The unknown object was observed with the naked eye, under good visibility conditions and followed a trajectory in the South / North direction.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.449. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador no Distrito Federal”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
